data.description: Do you like pina coladas & dancing in the rain? Welcome to Little Gasparilla Island! Little Gasparilla Island is true island living because the only way to access it is by boat! How neat is that! No cars, just boats, bikes, fishing poles, golfcarts, coconuts and salt. The home is as unique and as special as the island it rest on. The two bedroom, three bathroom home sits directly on the bay with a private dock and 12,000 lb boat lift (photos to come). The dock has water and filet station. The 672 sq ft deck has plenty of room for entertaining. Fully funished. Call now for your private showing. (The dock HOA is optional. The additional dock is right next to the private dock. First come for dock space/$150 annually).
